headline: Unpacking Q4 Earnings: Ollie's (NASDAQ:OLLI) In The Context Of Other Discount Retailer Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how discount retailer stocks fared in Q4, starting with Ollie's (NASDAQ:OLLI).
